i%E1%BB%83u-thu-ng%C3%A2m/poem-Ejpz7xbo08hHqQXq94Ph-A">Phụng hoạ Lỗ Vọng nhàn cư tạp đề - Hiểu thu ngâm - 奉和魯望閑居雜題—曉秋吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-H%C6%B0u/author-YaU63-B8n1CAEl8OjKg7AQ">Bì Nhật Hưu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-T%C4%A9nh/Tam-%C4%90i%E1%BB%87p-s%C6%A1n/poem-8vgQ7q-vo6tfSsMEVIjVcA">Tam Điệp sơn - 三疊山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-T%C4%A9nh/author-QsXB3NJ2bDAOYiQOgeyy4w">Nguyễn Văn Tĩnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-t%C3%AA-h%C3%A0nh/poem-xfZ_mXirWBP-Q9n6y0q8NQ">Thạch tê hành - 石犀行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-ng%C3%A2m/poem-A7bqmZ6MNjzOfeJcMvCNqg">Trường ngâm - 長吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/T%E1%BB%B1-c%E1%BB%95-ch%C6%B0-tri%E1%BA%BFt-nh%C3%A2n/poem-AcafTrS8O_a9zrO1myLsZg">Tự cổ chư triết nhân - 自古諸哲人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-S%C6%A1n/author-o98HuijKnTRKdgvHyXbEYw">Hàn Sơn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
